      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable entry point for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone needing basic transportation on a budget. This vehicle is being offered as a value-focused project/work car with evident cosmetic and wear-related needs, but it presents a practical opportunity for someone who sees the upside in an inexpensive purchase. Priced to move and ideal for buyers looking for low upfront cost with room to improve over time.",
