      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest little car that\u2019s a great fit for someone needing affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. It shows its age and isn\u2019t a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and can still be a handy commuter, backup car, or first project for someone who likes tinkering. If you\u2019re looking for dependable basic transportation at a sensible price from a straightforward seller, this one is worth a look.",
