    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project with strong bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. This car presents in driver/project condition, but it still offers a well-sorted platform with responsive steering feel, a straightforward mechanical layout, and the kind of chassis that rewards a little effort. Engine starts and runs, transmission engages, and it has the makings of a dependable budget commuter, weekend tinkering build, or parts-friendly restoration candidate. Not perfect cosmetically and will want attention, but for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance, this is an affordable entry point into a capable, honest-used car with real potential.",
      "price": 6950.0,
